            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "An asteroid louse can eat objects with a hardness of 10 or lower. It deals 1 damage per minute to an object it\u2019s consuming. An asteroid louse is sated and stops feeding on a given day after dealing 100 damage this way.",
